<scenario>
The agent A provided the following violation scenario:
The call to MHD_DLOG invokes daemon->custom_error_log (a user-supplied callback). If that callback calls MHD_quiesce_daemon (directly or via other functions), then MHD_quiesce_daemon → MHD_DLOG → custom_error_log → MHD_quiesce_daemon forms an indirect recursion cycle, violating Rule 17.2.
</scenario>
